Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF SAN FRANCISCO, MUNICIPALITY OF ZARAGOZA, PROVINCE OF NUEVA ECIJA, TO THAT OF GENERAL LUNA.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 27, September 08, 1936 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF SAN FRANCISCO, MUNICIPALITY OF ZARAGOZA, PROVINCE OF NUEVA ECIJA, TO THAT OF GENERAL LUNA.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of San Francisco, of the municipality of Zaragoza, Province of Nueva Ecija, is hereby changed to that of General Luna.
Section 2.(aw√ûhi( This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, September 8, 1936
